        "subject": {
          "reference": "urn:uuid:11111111-1111-4111-8111-111111111111"
        },
        "payload": [
          {
            "contentString": "{patientName} is a 38-year-old man in the Czech Republic who appears guarded and distracted during interview, with limited emotional expression and periods of inappropriate affect [MEDLINEPLUS:F20.9, SNOMED:F20.9]. He reports hearing voices that others do not hear and says they sometimes become frightening enough that he covers his ears and tries to isolate himself [MEDLINEPLUS:F20.9, MEDDIALOG:F20.9:3]. He also describes fixed beliefs that other people are trying to hurt or control him, including fear that hidden devices are monitoring him [MEDLINEPLUS:F20.9, MEDDIALOG:F20.9:7]. At times his speech becomes hard to follow, with disorganized thought content and odd phrases that do not make sense [MEDLINEPLUS:F20.9, SNOMED:F20.9, MEDDIALOG:F20.9:7].\n\nOver the last several years, {patientName} has become increasingly withdrawn and antisocial, spending much of the day alone at home and struggling to maintain regular work [MEDLINEPLUS:F20.9, MEDDIALOG:F20.9:7]. Friends have largely drifted away because he mistrusts other people and avoids social contact [MEDLINEPLUS:F20.9, MEDDIALOG:F20.9:7]. His daily routine is inconsistent; he often has difficulty organizing tasks, making decisions, and managing basic responsibilities without prompting [MEDLINEPLUS:F20.9].\n\nHe lives with family members who remain involved in his care, but relationships are strained by his suspicion that relatives may wish to harm him [MEDDIALOG:F20.9:7]. Family members describe episodes of chanting in nonsensical language and writing strange notes, which fit with disorganized thought and language disturbance [MEDDIALOG:F20.9:7, SNOMED:F20.9]. He has few current hobbies beyond sitting alone in his room, occasionally listening to music, and taking short walks when persuaded by his family; these lifestyle details are clinically plausible defaults."
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "fullUrl": "urn:uuid:0ea51c10-5f10-4408-a2d4-572e28d113d7",
